<div class="nine wide column">
<h1>Make sure the internet <br>never loses. <span style="color:#fff">Ever.</span></h1>
<p>The <a href="http://www.sopastrike.com/" target="_blank">Internet Blackout</a> was just the beginning. On <a href="https://www.battleforthenet.com/july12" target="_blank">July 12th</a>, we need to join together to protect net neutrality. Together, our websites and personal networks can mobilize the planet to defend free speech &amp; free choice online. The <a href="https://www.privateinternetaccess.com/blog/2017/06/private-internet-access-shines-cat-signal-net-neutrality" target="_blank">#CatSignal</a> has been activated. Are you in?</p>
</div>
